header.description: No header dataset required—this report has no scalar tokens.

rows.description: System metrics aggregated by minute: CPU, memory, disk I/O, network I/O, and process-level metrics.

totals.description: No totals dataset required—this report has no totals tokens.

semantics: All tokens are pass-through—no parameters or filters required. The report renders all rows from the app_metrics_system_minute table in chronological order.
transformations: No transformations needed—each token maps directly to a single column in the source table.
